sql:
SELECT AVG(temperature), AVG(humidity)
FROM forecast_data
WHERE forecast_accuracy < 0.9 AND forecast_confidence <> 'high';

SELECT station_id, MAX(maintenance_date) AS latest_maintenance_date
FROM weather_station_maintenance
GROUP BY station_id;

SELECT weather_condition
FROM weather_data
WHERE station_id = (
  SELECT MAX(station_id)
  FROM weather_stations
);

external_knowledge:
1. A comfortable temperature range for humans is generally between 20 and 30 degrees Celsius;
2. 'Good accuracy rate' refers to forecast accuracy greater than 70%;
3. Meteorological stations are specialized for weather prediction.
